";}s:18:"_intro_description";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e528cb03c";}s:5:"intro";a:1:{i:0;s:0:"";}s:6:"_intro";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7da3d85a48";}s:33:"service_details_card_0_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:36:"Employment Contracts and Agreements:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_0_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_0_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:309:"Our lawyers assist with the drafting, review, and negotiation of employment contracts, ensuring that the terms and conditions are clear, fair, and legally enforceable. We help employers and employees establish agreements that protect their rights, address key obligations, and mitigate potential disputes.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_0_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_1_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:37:"Discrimination and Harassment Claims:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_1_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_1_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:322:"If you believe you have been subjected to discrimination or harassment in the workplace, our experienced lawyers can guide you through the process of filing a claim. We provide zealous representation in cases involving gender, race, age, disability, sexual orientation, and other forms of discrimination or harassment.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_1_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_2_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:23:"Wage and Hour Disputes:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_2_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_2_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:322:"We assist both employers and employees in resolving wage and hour disputes. Our lawyers are well-versed in federal, provincial, and local laws governing minimum wage, overtime, employee classification, and other wage-related issues. We work diligently to protect your rights and ensure compliance with applicable laws.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_2_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_3_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:34:"Workplace Policies and Compliance:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_3_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_3_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:366:"We help employers establish comprehensive workplace policies that align with current labor and employment laws. Our lawyers provide guidance on compliance with regulations, including health and safety standards, non-discrimination requirements, and privacy laws. We also conduct audits and provide training to promote a respectful and compliant work environment.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_3_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_4_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:35:"Wrongful Termination and Severance:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_4_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_4_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:308:"If you have been wrongfully terminated or need assistance negotiating severance packages, our lawyers can advocate for your rights. We assess the circumstances surrounding your termination, evaluate potential claims, and pursue legal action to seek appropriate remedies or negotiate fair severance terms.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_4_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_5_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:30:"Employment Dispute Resolution:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_5_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_5_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:346:"Our team is experienced in alternative dispute resolution methods, such as mediation and arbitration. We strive to resolve employment disputes efficiently and amicably, minimizing the time, cost, and disruption associated with litigation. However, when litigation is necessary, we provide strong representation in employment-related lawsuits.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_5_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:33:"service_details_card_6_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:17:"Labour Relations:";}s:34:"_service_details_card_6_card_title";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e6031bb8e";}s:35:"service_details_card_6_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:289:"For employers dealing with labor unions or employees seeking to exercise their rights to collective bargaining, our lawyers provide guidance on labor relations matters. We assist with negotiations, contract disputes, unfair labor practices, and other issues related to labor relations.

";}s:36:"_service_details_card_6_card_content";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e60f1bb8f";}s:20:"service_details_card";a:1:{i:0;s:1:"7";}s:21:"_service_details_card";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7e5d41bb8d";}s:25:"outro_0_outro_description";a:1:{i:0;s:274:"At Capital Street Law, we are dedicated to protecting the rights and interests of both employers and employees in employment law matters. Our lawyers provide personalized attention, strategic advice, and strong advocacy to achieve the best possible outcomes for our clients.";}s:26:"_outro_0_outro_description";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7f03dcc126";}s:25:"outro_1_outro_description";a:1:{i:0;s:251:"Contact us today to schedule a consultation with one of our experienced employment law lawyers. We are here to listen, understand your unique circumstances, and provide you with effective legal solutions tailored to your specific employment law needs.";}s:26:"_outro_1_outro_description";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7f03dcc126";}s:5:"outro";a:1:{i:0;s:1:"2";}s:6:"_outro";a:1:{i:0;s:19:"field_64a7f012cc125";}}}